attributes.title: Waste of space
attributes.review: I was so looking forward to having this app and then as soon as it downloaded my screen froze and crashed. The software has the worst bug in it that I’ve seen and I code for a living. There are so many things wrong with this app I cannot even begin to explain how you could fix it other than dismembering the whole platform. Multiple viruses are working through the app at once. When you are asked to put your personal information in, I ended up getting so many called and email and texts from random businesses and scammers. It uses all your phones battery and is not updating with news on how we as trump supporters can ruin this country even more. There’s truly nothing else to do with this app other than get rid of it along with all the other ridiculous and uneducated users that it comes with.
